reviews.review_text:
Very fast show These recordings are famous from this late summer tour. Phil is  very defined and the mix is very good. This show cooks at breakneck speed the entire night, it is almost too fast at points.  A high energy Jack Straw gets things happening. Very good TLEO too. FOTD and Let It  Grow are stand outs. Set two short  first half but Samson & Terrapin are excellent.
The Other One is really intense as is the rest of the show. Sweet Baby Blue
Yellow Light - Ghost Dance Amazing show - venue.. drove from SLC after Dinosaurs show on the Great Salt Lake.. To see Robert Hunter and Jerry back to back.. gone are the days...
